  m_Name: Death - First Encounter
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  data:
    convoName: Death - First Encounter
    lines:
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: 'I suppose time has rendered you soft. You would have struck with Isovios
        as soon as you saw me eons ago. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "Trust me. I\u2019ll do just that if you don\u2019t start explaining. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "\u2026 "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: 'The passing of life is mesmerizing. It is the end of a story, the conclusion
        of a dream, the finale of a journey that may not feel satisfactory. The start
        of a new era. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'What the hell are you? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "Not only have you killed, you\u2019ve inflicted chaos and sowed suffering.
        I\u2019ve seen countless people ascend around you, their souls regretful,
        enraged, and miserable. Humanity was simply a stepping stone for you. A tool,
        nothing else. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "So, then\u2026 you\u2019ve come for me at last\u2026 Death. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: 'I do not kill; I merely guide the dead. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "\u2026 "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "Perhaps it was the time which had passed through you that made you more\u2026
        willing. Despite your crimes against humanity, you are not beyond redemption. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'Redemption? I simply achieved what every man could only fantasize about,
        immortality. Compared to those mortals, I am akin to a god walking this planet!
        How does the existence of insignificant maggots matter? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "A god? You are but a human who stood on the bodies of billions\u2013 "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'But omnipotent nonetheless! Through those trivial lives, I could vanquish
        any threats that came my way. I was no longer afraid. I no longer had a reason
        to be afraid! I had conquered death! I had conquered you! '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "\u2026 "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: 'Go through the door and you will witness your worst atrocities. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'You mean my achievements? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "\u2026 "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: 'Clearly, what I have provided is inadequate. I will endow you with a
        portion of my powers. I hope this will be enough. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
